[SQUEALING] Yes, Papa! We're coming!

2082
02:32:40,402 --> 02:32:42,362
[GIGGLING]

2083
02:32:56,043 --> 02:32:57,919
[SOBBING]

2084
02:32:58,879 --> 02:33:01,965
Come on, Billy.
